      <section eId="sec_48_13_94">
        <num>48-13-94</num>
        <content>
          <p>Each person collecting the tax authorized by this article shall be allowed a percentage of the tax due and accounted for and shall be reimbursed in the form of a deduction in submitting, reporting, and paying the amount due if the amount due is not delinquent at the time of payment. The rate of deduction shall be 3 percent of the amount due but only if the amount due was not delinquent at the time of payment.</p>
